        "text": "9. Through Hull University (and the OR Society) I met systems lecturer, Giles Hindle. He told me that his children were **unschool**ed. He let them do what they want. I said what if they do nothing? He said they'll experience the consequences. He waits for them to ask him questions then he asks them how they would answer the question! His daughter is into horses and so that is what she does. I guess that is the same as we learnt from age 0 to school!"
